<template>
    <GChart
      type="PieChart"
      :data="chartData"
      :options="chartOptions"
    />
  </template>
      
      <script>
  import { GChart } from "vue-google-charts";
  
  export default {
    name: "GoogleChart",
    components: {
      GChart,
    },
    data() {
      return {
        chartData: [
        ['Age', 'Weight'],
          [ 8,      12],
          [ 4,      5.5],
          [ 11,     14],
          [ 4,      5],
          [ 3,      3.5],
          [ 6.5,    7]
        ],
  
        chartOptions: {
          legend: "none",
          is3D: true,
          // pieSliceText: "none",
          height: 600,
  
          backgroundColor: "rgb(154, 155, 157)",
  
          slices: {
            4: { offset: 0.3 },
            9: { offset: 0.1 },
            6: { offset: 0.4 },
            5: { offset: 0.5 },
          },
        },
      };
    },
  };
  </script>
